trans-unit.source: Represents the properties of an <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Representerer egenskapene for en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan ikke arves.

trans-unit.source: The AutoGeneratedFieldProperties class is used by data-bound controls to specify the properties of an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField> object when creating an automatically generated field.
trans-unit.target: Klassen AutoGeneratedFieldProperties brukes av databundet kontroller til å angi egenskaper for en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField>objekt når du oppretter en automatisk generert felt.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField>

trans-unit.source: For example, when the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView> control creates an automatically generated row, it creates an AutoGeneratedFieldProperties object with the row's properties and passes it to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView.CreateAutoGeneratedRow%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel når den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView>kontrollen oppretter en automatisk generert rad, oppretter du en AutoGeneratedFieldProperties-objekt med den raden egenskaper, og sender den til den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView.CreateAutoGeneratedRow%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView.CreateAutoGeneratedRow%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView>

trans-unit.source: Likewise, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> control passes an AutoGeneratedFieldProperties object to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.CreateAutoGeneratedColumn%2A> method when creating an automatically generated column.
trans-unit.target: På samme måte i <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>kontrollen sender et AutoGeneratedFieldProperties-objekt til den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.CreateAutoGeneratedColumn%2A>metoden når du oppretter en automatisk generert kolonne.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.CreateAutoGeneratedColumn%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > This class is typically used only when extending the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> or <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView> control.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Denne klassen brukes vanligvis under utvidelse av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>eller <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>

trans-unit.source: You can specify the name of the field to bind to an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField> object by setting the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedFieldProperties.DataField%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Du kan angi navnet på feltet skal bindes til en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField>objektet ved å angi den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedFieldProperties.DataField%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedFieldProperties.DataField%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField>

trans-unit.source: To specify the data type of the field values, set the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedFieldProperties.Type%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil angi datatypen for feltverdiene, angitt i <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedFieldProperties.Type%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedFieldProperties.Type%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can prevent users from modifying the field values by setting the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedFieldProperties.IsReadOnly%2A> property to `true`.
trans-unit.target: Du kan hindre brukere i å endre feltverdiene ved å angi den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedFieldProperties.IsReadOnly%2A>egenskapen `true`.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedFieldProperties.IsReadOnly%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can also assign a name to an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField> object by setting the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedFieldProperties.Name%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Du kan også tilordne et navn som en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField>objektet ved å angi den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedFieldProperties.Name%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedFieldProperties.Name%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedFieldProperties"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedFieldProperties"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Use this constructor to create a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedFieldProperties> class.
trans-unit.target: Bruk denne konstruktøren til å opprette en ny forekomst av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedFieldProperties>klassen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedFieldProperties>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > This constructor is primarily used by control developers when extending a data-bound control.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Denne konstruktøren brukes hovedsakelig av kontrollutviklere når utvider en databundet-kontroll.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the name of the field bound to the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir navnet på feltet bundet til den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: Use the DataField property to specify the name of the data field to bind to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField> object.
trans-unit.target: Bruk DataField-egenskapen til å angi navnet på datafeltet skal bindes til det <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField>objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField> object automatically displays the values in the appropriate control, based on the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedFieldProperties.Type%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField>objektet viser automatisk verdiene i den aktuelle kontrollen, basert på den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedFieldProperties.Type%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedFieldProperties.Type%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField>

trans-unit.source: For example, <xref:System.Boolean> values are displayed in check box controls, while <xref:System.String> values are displayed as plain text.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel <xref:System.Boolean>verdiene vises i avmerkingsboksen Kontroller mens <xref:System.String>verdiene vises som ren tekst.</xref:System.String> </xref:System.Boolean>

trans-unit.source: The name of the field bound to the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på feltet som er bundet til den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is an empty string (""), which indicates that this property is not set.
trans-unit.target: Standarden er en tom streng (""), noe som angir at denne egenskapen ikke er angitt.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating whether the values displayed in an <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField"></xref> object can be modified in edit mode.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om verdiene som vises i en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField"> </xref> objektet kan endres i redigeringsmodus.

trans-unit.source: Use the IsReadOnly property to specify whether the values of the field bound to an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField> object can be modified in edit mode.
trans-unit.target: Bruk IsReadOnly-egenskapen til å angi om verdiene i feltet bundet til en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField>objektet kan endres i redigeringsmodus.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField>

trans-unit.source: When a data-bound control is in edit mode, fields that are read-only are displayed as plain text, without any editing controls.
trans-unit.target: Når en databundet kontroll i redigeringsmodus, vises feltene som er skrivebeskyttet som ren tekst, uten noen redigering kontroller.

trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>for å angi at verdiene er skrivebeskyttet. Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The name is often the name of the field bound to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField> object.

trans-unit.source: The value of this property is also displayed in the header section of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField> object in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView> or a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> control.
trans-unit.target: Verdien for denne egenskapen også vises i topp-delen av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField>objekt i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView>eller <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField>

trans-unit.source: Use the Type property to specify the data type of the value displayed in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField> object.

trans-unit.source: The data type determines what type of control is rendered in an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField> object to display the value.
trans-unit.target: Datatypen bestemmer hvilken type kontroll gjengis i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField>objekt for å vise verdien.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField>

trans-unit.source: For example, a check box control is displayed when the type is <xref:System.Boolean>.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel skal en avmerkingsbokskontrollen vises når typen er <xref:System.Boolean>.</xref:System.Boolean>
